Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points

Class FillingArrayPointsReadValues<T extends java.lang.Number>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points.FillingArrayPointsReadValues<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FillingArray<Point<T>>, Filling<Array<Point<T>>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FillingArrayPointsReadDoubleNumbers, FillingArrayPointsReadIntegerNumbers
    public abstract class FillingArrayPointsReadValues<T extends java.lang.Number>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FillingArray<Point<T>>
    The class is the root of the class hierarchy that implements the contract declared in the FillingArrayPoints interface of the filling of objects of Array class and classical arrays with an object of the Point class with numeric coordinates using the data read by the object of the class Reader encapsulated in this class.

    Created by Konstantin Lugowoy on 27-Jan-18.

    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Konsytantin Lugowoy
